1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,740
=Episode 9=

3
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:04,359
I had Feng Liu prepare

4
00:01:04,359 --> 00:01:06,200
all these nice ornaments for you.

5
00:01:09,359 --> 00:01:10,319
They're all yours.

6
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:14,799
If you're trying to make amends,

7
00:01:14,799 --> 00:01:15,640
don't bother.

8
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:17,200
That's not my intention.

9
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:18,719
It's just...

10
00:01:18,719 --> 00:01:19,599
Right.

11
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:22,239
You would never apologize to anyone.

12
00:01:22,560 --> 00:01:22,879
I...

13
00:01:22,879 --> 00:01:24,040
You must be

14
00:01:25,480 --> 00:01:27,040
wanting me to choose one

15
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:28,799
as a concealed weapon.

16
00:01:28,799 --> 00:01:29,799
From now on,

17
00:01:29,799 --> 00:01:31,239
it'll help me deal with Rong Zhaohua.

18
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,640
Then I won't hold back.

19
00:01:34,719 --> 00:01:35,159
I...

20
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:10,639
I...

21
00:02:10,879 --> 00:02:11,280
I...

22
00:02:12,479 --> 00:02:13,599
I thought...

23
00:02:15,599 --> 00:02:16,159
Never mind.

24
00:02:19,080 --> 00:02:21,039
My Lord,
you've been acting strange lately.

25
00:02:21,039 --> 00:02:22,159
Could it be

26
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:24,599
that something's happened
with Rong Zhaohua?

27
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:26,080
No.

28
00:02:31,719 --> 00:02:32,759
I had the servants

29
00:02:32,759 --> 00:02:33,800
build this birdcage

30
00:02:34,039 --> 00:02:35,280
and leave this window open

31
00:02:35,599 --> 00:02:37,319
so the bird can come and go freely.

32
00:02:38,919 --> 00:02:39,960
Why have you been

33
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:42,080
so fixated on birdcages lately?

34
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,960
I was thinking of giving it

35
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:51,039
a designated spot

36
00:02:52,479 --> 00:02:53,080
to do its business,

37
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,560
so it doesn't dirty my room.

38
00:03:02,759 --> 00:03:04,039
I also had the servants

39
00:03:04,319 --> 00:03:05,919
prepare some Zhao Tribe pastries
for you.

40
00:03:06,319 --> 00:03:07,319
I know it's been a while

41
00:03:07,319 --> 00:03:08,400
since you left the Zhao Tribe.

42
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,560
You must miss it.

43
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,280
Besides my elder sister,

44
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:14,120
I have no attachment to the Zhao Tribe.

45
00:03:15,159 --> 00:03:15,960
But...

46
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:17,479
My Lord.

47
00:03:26,479 --> 00:03:27,400
Wait for me a moment.

48
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,080
Holy...

49
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:52,719
Holy Maiden...

50
00:03:53,159 --> 00:03:53,520
I...

51
00:03:56,879 --> 00:03:57,599
What's the situation?

52
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,360
My Lord,

53
00:03:58,759 --> 00:03:59,639
the Nanfeng spy reports

54
00:03:59,879 --> 00:04:01,080
that Rong Xiu sent men to the Shen manor

55
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,599
and brought Minister Shen's wife

56
00:04:02,599 --> 00:04:03,560
and children here.

57
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,199
Proceed as planned.

58
00:04:10,159 --> 00:04:10,599
Yes.

59
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,120
Hey.

60
00:04:18,439 --> 00:04:19,560
(Just as I thought,)

61
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:22,160
(this time he's going after Rong Xiu.)

62
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:34,600
Minister Shen, you are not eating.

63
00:04:34,839 --> 00:04:35,480
What's wrong?

64
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,879
Is the food

65
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,160
not to your liking?

66
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:41,959
General.

67
00:04:42,279 --> 00:04:43,000
Minister Shen's wife

68
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:43,959
and child have arrived.

69
00:04:45,199 --> 00:04:46,480
General, why are you doing this?

70
00:04:47,199 --> 00:04:48,600
With such a lavish feast,

71
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:50,399
shouldn't your wife and child try some?

72
00:04:50,959 --> 00:04:51,800
What a waste.

73
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:52,879
Come, sit.

74
00:04:58,519 --> 00:04:59,319
Come on.

75
00:04:59,839 --> 00:05:00,480
Eat up.

76
00:05:04,519 --> 00:05:05,199
General Rong.

77
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,839
The people gave their lives

78
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:13,079
for the grain in Changzhou's
charity granary.

79
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:24,079
Come here.

80
00:05:27,959 --> 00:05:28,879
Open up.

81
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:51,560
(Why isn't his man here?)

82
00:05:57,199 --> 00:05:58,120
What are you doing here?

83
00:06:00,639 --> 00:06:02,720
I'm here for the same reason

84
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,839
you are.

85
00:06:03,839 --> 00:06:05,519
Tonight's mission is dangerous.

86
00:06:05,839 --> 00:06:06,399
Go back.

87
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:07,839
It seems

88
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:10,240
it's not that I don't trust you.

89
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,879
It's that you don't trust me.

90
00:06:12,279 --> 00:06:13,720
This has nothing to do with trust.

91
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:14,879
I have my own plans.

92
00:06:14,879 --> 00:06:15,680
Then

93
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,879
I won't trouble you either.

94
00:06:17,879 --> 00:06:19,040
I have my own plans too.

95
00:06:21,279 --> 00:06:22,600
This place is full of traps.

96
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,959
If you don't know them beforehand,

97
00:06:23,959 --> 00:06:25,199
even with the Divine Power,

98
00:06:25,199 --> 00:06:26,319
you won't get far.

99
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:34,920
Fine.

100
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:36,959
Since you're here, stay.

101
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,199
My Lord,

102
00:06:41,199 --> 00:06:42,560
what do you need me to do?

103
00:06:44,879 --> 00:06:46,480
Rong Xiu's rise to power

104
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,199
wasn't just due to military merit.

105
00:06:48,439 --> 00:06:50,800
He's been forming factions
and eliminating rivals.

106
00:06:51,519 --> 00:06:52,399
Because Minister Shen

107
00:06:52,399 --> 00:06:54,199
refused to turn relief grain
into military supplies,

108
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,639
he locked his family here.

109
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,120
Tonight,

110
00:06:58,399 --> 00:06:59,600
all we have to do is rescue them

111
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:01,160
and expose the truth.

112
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:03,680
Even if His Majesty wants
to protect him,

113
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,160
with the court in uproar,

114
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,240
he'll have no excuse.

115
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:09,399
What's the plan?

116
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:13,079
See those soldiers?

117
00:07:13,519 --> 00:07:15,240
Use the Divine Power to draw them away,

118
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:16,560
then go in and rescue them.

119
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:05,600
We walked into a trap.

120
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:17,040
You really thought I'd be unprepared?

121
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:19,040
Tonight,

122
00:08:19,399 --> 00:08:21,720
you're not leaving alive.

123
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:31,000
Come on.

124
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,679
Come at me, all of you.

125
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:35,159
I am the Lord Nine-Thousand of Kun.

126
00:08:35,159 --> 00:08:36,639
After you kill me,

127
00:08:36,639 --> 00:08:38,039
how will you explain

128
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:39,320
to His Majesty?

129
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:48,200
Lord Nine-Thousand broke
into the general's manor

130
00:08:48,679 --> 00:08:50,200
and attacked first.

131
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:52,639
I had no choice but to defend myself
with my guards

132
00:08:52,639 --> 00:08:53,879
in the name of justice.

133
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,159
How's that?

134
00:08:56,399 --> 00:08:57,200
Rong Xiu,

135
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:00,000
you even killed your own men.

136
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,679
To achieve greatness,

137
00:09:02,279 --> 00:09:03,600
one must not be bound by trivialities.

138
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:06,000
They were my guards,

139
00:09:06,519 --> 00:09:07,799
so they should be ready

140
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:09,720
to die for me at any moment.

141
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:13,000
You all saw that, didn't you?

142
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,759
This is your commander.

143
00:09:15,039 --> 00:09:16,320
You see him as your faith.

144
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:16,960
Yet he sees you

145
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:19,360
as expendable pawns.

146
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:21,240
Are you sure you want to keep
serving him?

147
00:09:21,799 --> 00:09:23,000
What are you waiting for?

148
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,759
Military orders are absolute.

149
00:09:25,159 --> 00:09:25,799
Attack!

150
00:09:34,679 --> 00:09:36,039
Everyone, stop!

151
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:37,200
General!

152
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:39,120
Your Grand General is now in my hands.

153
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,240
All alone.

154
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,480
Even if you have the General,

155
00:09:41,639 --> 00:09:42,919
you won't leave this manor.

156
00:09:42,919 --> 00:09:45,519
Who said I wanted to leave?

157
00:09:46,799 --> 00:09:48,519
I'm going inside.

158
00:09:48,679 --> 00:09:50,279
Clear a path for me.

159
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:52,440
I'm going into the side chamber.

160
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:27,399
Stop.

161
00:10:58,639 --> 00:10:59,320
How is it?

162
00:11:00,519 --> 00:11:01,440
Still no.

163
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:03,840
Rong Xiu is too strong-willed.

164
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:06,120
His criminal evidence is crucial to him.

165
00:11:06,879 --> 00:11:07,919
I can't read it.

166
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:19,919
A whole night has passed.

167
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:23,200
Not only did you fail to control me,

168
00:11:23,759 --> 00:11:25,919
but you'll also be charged
with breaking into a general's manor.

169
00:11:25,919 --> 00:11:27,240
Once the court convenes,

170
00:11:28,559 --> 00:11:29,919
let's see

171
00:11:29,919 --> 00:11:31,840
how you explain this.

172
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:32,440
You...

173
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:33,799
You don't need to wait for court.

174
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:36,360
The Emperor's token is here.

175
00:11:36,620 --> 00:11:37,000
(Decree)

176
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:38,879
(Decree)
Surrender now!

177
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:43,120
Brother.

178
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:44,519
I'm late.

179
00:11:44,799 --> 00:11:45,480
Zhaohua!

180
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:47,159
Why are you here?

181
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:49,879
I couldn't sleep last night.

182
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:52,200
I had a bad feeling about you.

183
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:53,600
When I came today

184
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:54,919
and sensed something wrong,

185
00:11:55,279 --> 00:11:57,720
I rushed to His Majesty
and got this decree.

186
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:58,799
You

187
00:11:58,799 --> 00:11:59,879
walked right into my trap.

188
00:12:00,399 --> 00:12:01,240
Take them away.

189
00:12:06,639 --> 00:12:07,120
Zhaohua,

190
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,720
I'm useless.

191
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:09,840
I made you worry.

192
00:12:10,399 --> 00:12:11,639
You and I are siblings.

193
00:12:11,639 --> 00:12:12,519
No need for words.

194
00:12:13,159 --> 00:12:13,600
Oh, right,

195
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:15,720
Minister Shen's wife and child,

196
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,000
are they secured?

197
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,120
I locked them

198
00:12:21,120 --> 00:12:22,639
in the confinement room
behind the study.

199
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:28,080
Only one key can open it.

200
00:12:35,159 --> 00:12:36,639
Good.

201
00:12:39,879 --> 00:12:40,480
Zhaohua,

202
00:12:42,039 --> 00:12:42,600
what's wrong?

203
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:54,120
General Rong,

204
00:12:54,519 --> 00:12:56,639
how do you like the dream

205
00:12:56,639 --> 00:12:57,879
I wove for you?

206
00:13:22,980 --> 00:13:24,380
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

207
00:13:24,860 --> 00:13:26,300
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

208
00:13:26,500 --> 00:13:29,620
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

209
00:13:29,940 --> 00:13:33,740
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

210
00:13:36,700 --> 00:13:38,420
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

211
00:13:38,420 --> 00:13:39,940
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

212
00:13:40,300 --> 00:13:43,700
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

213
00:13:43,700 --> 00:13:47,700
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

214
00:13:48,860 --> 00:13:52,020
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

215
00:13:52,020 --> 00:13:55,580
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

216
00:13:55,580 --> 00:13:57,900
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

217
00:13:57,900 --> 00:14:02,100
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

218
00:14:02,540 --> 00:14:04,180
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

219
00:14:04,180 --> 00:14:05,700
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

220
00:14:05,700 --> 00:14:08,900
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

221
00:14:09,300 --> 00:14:11,220
♪In dreams, it's you♪

222
00:14:11,220 --> 00:14:12,620
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

223
00:14:12,620 --> 00:14:15,940
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

224
00:14:15,940 --> 00:14:19,340
♪I can't forget
the stars in your eyes♪

225
00:14:19,340 --> 00:14:22,900
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

226
00:14:22,900 --> 00:14:26,140
♪In this mortal world,
there is only us♪

227
00:14:26,140 --> 00:14:29,580
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
